General.Name: Fentura Financial Inc
General.Description: Fentura Financial, Inc. operates as the bank holding company for The State Bank that provides banking products and services to individuals, small businesses, and government entities. It offers deposit products, such as checking, savings, and term certificate accounts; and lending products that includes residential mortgage, commercial real estate, commercial, home equity, and consumer loans. The company was founded in 1898 and is headquartered in Fenton, Michigan.
